OL,3,CGovernment to appeal Legacy Act
OL,4,C'unlawful' ruling
OL,6,FThe UK Government has announced it is
OL,7,Fto appeal a ruling by the High Court
OL,8,Fin Belfast that one of the key
OL,9,Felements of the Northern Ireland
OL,10,FTroubles Legacy Act is unlawful.
OL,12,FLast week, Mr Justice Adrian Colton
OL,13,Fruled that the provision for
OL,14,Fconditional immunity from prosecution
OL,15,Ffor Troubles offences in the
OL,16,Flegislation is not compliant with the
OL,17,FEuropean Convention on Human Rights
OL,18,F(ECHR).
