OL,6,FThe judge also said there is no
OL,7,Fevidence that the immunity provision
OL,8,Fwill in any way contribute to
OL,9,Freconciliation in Northern Ireland.
OL,11,FHowever, he did rule that a new body
OL,12,Fset up to probe Troubles killings
OL,13,Fcould carry out human rights-compliant
OL,14,Finvestigations.
OL,16,FNorthern Ireland Secretary Chris
OL,17,FHeaton-Harris then said the government
OL,18,F"will consider Mr Justice Colton's
OL,19,Ffindings very, very carefully", but
OL,20,Fadded that ministers "remain committed
OL,21,Fto implementing the Legacy Act".
