OL,6,F"We remain committed to implementing
OL,7,Fthe Legacy Act and delivering the
OL,8,FIndependent Commission for
OL,9,FReconciliation and Information
OL,10,FRecovery (ICRIR) to provide better
OL,11,Foutcomes for victims and survivors of
OL,12,Fthe Troubles by giving them more
OL,13,Finformation about what happened to
OL,14,Ftheir loved ones."
OL,16,FThe Act received royal assent in
OL,17,FSeptember despite widespread
OL,18,Fopposition from political parties,
OL,19,Fvictims' organisations in Northern
OL,20,FIreland, and the Irish Government.
